text: Gabriela Barros Tapia (born 28 November 1980) is a Chilean actress and model who won Miss Universo Chile 2004 and represented Chile at Miss Universe 2004, placing in the top 15. ==Miss Universe 2004== Barros represented Chile at Miss Universe 2004 held in Quito, Ecuador, where she earned a spot in the top 15. The eventual winner was Miss Australia, Jennifer Hawkins. It was Chile's first placement since 1990.
